BRD (Business Requirement Document)
Project Name
Internship Selection Dashboard

Objective
The dashboard helps analyze:


Candidate performance


Selection trends


Department analysis


Internship insights



Dashboard Page 1 — Overview Dashboard
KPIs
KPI 1 — Total Candidates
Formula:
Total Candidates = COUNT('Table'[Candidate_ID])

KPI 2 — Selected Candidates
Formula:
Selected Candidates =CALCULATE(    COUNT('Table'[Candidate_ID]),    'Table'[Selection_Status] = "Selected")

KPI 3 — Selection Rate %
Formula:
Selection Rate % =DIVIDE(    [Selected Candidates],    [Total Candidates]) * 100

KPI 4 — Average Performance Score
Formula:
Average Performance Score =AVERAGE('Table'[Performance_Score])

